snippet.title: Disney Dreamlight Valley - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Discover the magic that memories hold as you embark on an enchanting journey, and explore rich stories in a village of your own design, alongside some of Disney and Pixar’s most beloved characters in this new life-sim adventure game. Welcome to Disney Dreamlight Valley.

Wishlist today at http://www.disneydreamlightvalley.com/ 

Join the community on:
Instagram: http://instagram.com/disneydreamlightvalley 
Twitter: http://twitter.com/DisneyDLV 
Facebook: http://facebook.com/DisneyDreamlightValley 
Discord: https://discord.gg/Q2PAkGJNBS 

#DisneyDreamlightValley #LiveMagically
